{"tid":255236,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"1440p 決戰 4k TV","createTime":"2017-05-23T18:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T21:26:19.000Z","uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4150a9f1cad82570d61fafe94270e065f8509952","tid":255236,"uid":75118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"由於我唔用電腦打機, 無買到Display Card,<br />\n一直以黎我都係靠Motherboard (Gigabyte H270) + CPU (i7 7700) 直出落 Dell U2515H, 開1440p 60 hz。<br />\n<br />\n不過, 前排買左部新4k電視(Samsung UA40KU6300)。<br />\n本身諗住買個HDMI Splitter, 將個Display訊號同時射向2k mon 同 4k電視度,<br />\n等兩個screen都有畫面出。<br />\n<br />\n但係, 我發現我個4k電視竟然出唔到1440p,<br />\n就算想custom 個 resolution出黎都唔得,<br />\n如下圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/020412_c5490701ade89127f598255873ad1e52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F020412_c5490701ade89127f598255873ad1e52.png&h=5da800b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/020420_481b600fc0c11ac6389ce05641aa3237.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F020420_481b600fc0c11ac6389ce05641aa3237.png&h=73f532d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/021635_1ae8a7ceb14db8bd125498b543371938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F021635_1ae8a7ceb14db8bd125498b543371938.jpg&h=e9e15680&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家, 如果想駁部電腦落個4k電視度的話,<br />\n只有兩個選擇:<br />\n1) 拔左原本Dell Mon條HDMI線, 再插4k電視條HDMI線落電腦, 然後再較返4k resolution<br />\n2) 將電腦個resolution由1440p降落去1080p, 以犧牲畫質黎換取畫面支援<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位, 有無方法可以解決到呢個問題, 喺保持1440p畫質嘅前題底下,<br />\n兩邊都出到畫面?<br />\n<br />\nThanks!!"},{"pid":"47fffc84da03fa3a06aa31f766f428332adc872b","tid":255236,"uid":4